{
  "texts": [
    "The program separates the image into numerous grids and forecasts each grid.",
    "This approach is fast but has poor detection accuracy.",
    "Ov2 14 has significantly improved in accuracy and speed when compared to YOLOv1.",
    "Ov2 employs DarkNet19 as a feature extraction network and combines training with target classification and detection to boost accuracy.",
    "However, YOLOv2 has just one detection branch, making it difficult to gather multi-scale context information."
  ]
}